    • Field Detail

      • parents

        public final PredictionContext[] parents
        Parent can be null only if full ctx mode and we make an array from PredictionContext.EMPTY and non-empty. We merge PredictionContext.EMPTY by using null parent and returnState == PredictionContext.EMPTY_RETURN_STATE.

      • returnStates

        public final int[] returnStates
        Sorted for merge, no duplicates; if present, PredictionContext.EMPTY_RETURN_STATE is always last.
